Trade/Device Name(s): SEJOY hCG One Step Pregnancy Test Strip
SEJOY hCG One Step Pregnancy Test Cassette
SEJOY hCG One Step Pregnancy Test Midstream
Submitter Information: Hangzhou Sejoy Electronics & Instruments Co., Ltd.
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for SEJOY hCG One Step Pregnancy Test in strip, cassette, and midstream formats for qualitative detection of hCG in urine.
Indications for Use Summary: A rapid, one-step lateral flow immunoassay for the qualitative detection of human chorionic gonadotropin (hCG) in urine to aid in the early detection of pregnancy.
